WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.980 --> 00:00:03.120
 Black Angus rib steak à la plancha 

00:00:05.120 --> 00:00:07.120
 Pre-heat the plancha to 180 ° C. 

00:00:09.180 --> 00:00:12.360
 Salt a side of the steak. 

00:00:20.780 --> 00:00:23.540
 Place the salted side on the plancha without oil. 

00:00:38.980 --> 00:00:42.060
 Let it slowly brown ... 

00:00:50.300 --> 00:00:53.680
 ... and turn the steak over. 

00:01:02.240 --> 00:01:05.820
 Salts the other side. 

00:01:21.300 --> 00:01:24.820
 Sprinkle pepper over it. 

00:01:36.140 --> 00:01:39.640
 Bake the steak 4 to 5 'depending on the thickness and turn it regularly. 

00:02:04.860 --> 00:02:08.380
 We get a beautiful color this way. 

